The Graph can fetch 1000 tokens per query. By default it's set to 100, but you can add `(first: 1000)` after the entity to expand that. 

If you want ALL tokens, you may need to set up a cursor:

Something like:

```
query tokens($name: string = {cursor}) {
  tokens(where {name_gt: $name}, orderBy: name, first:1000) {
    id
    symbol
    name
  }
}
```

